**Earth** is the [third planet](./Planet) from the Sun.

## History

Formed long ago. See [the overview](https://example.org/overview).

- accretion of [planetesimal](./planetesimal)s
- differentiation into a [core](./planetary_core)

The planet has **two** moons.

